A thought experiment for creating arbitrarily large integers.

This is just a learning exercise, not intended for use.

Dependencies
-------
* https://github.com/ericherman/libehstr
  (hex-to-decimal and decimal-to-hex string conversion)

Also, the tests depend upon libecheck
* https://github.com/ericherman/libecheck


